divs: Sighting DetailsLast night, I was walking down the beach, looking up at the sky when I saw ten objects which did not seem star like. I recorded the time of the event as approximately 21:15. I stayed and viewed the ten objects, some of which moved slowly and others which slowed down and speeded up. They moved from West to East. I stayed and watched for approximately 30 minutes before I left. I obtained a photograph of what I saw which is attached to this report.

Summary: A couple of UFOs in the skies above Lowestoft.
